snippet: Fourth seed Rafa Nadal was stunned by Serb Viktor Troicki in an upset-filled Shanghai Masters second round on Wednesday while Andy Murray breezed past American Steve Johnson and Nick Kyrgios slumped to a listless defeat....
lead_paragraph: Fourth seed Rafa Nadal was stunned by Serb Viktor Troicki in an upset-filled Shanghai Masters second round on Wednesday while Andy Murray breezed past American Steve Johnson and Nick Kyrgios slumped to a listless defeat.

headline.print_headline: Nadal Stunned, Murray Cruises, Kyrgios Slumps in Shanghai
headline.main: Nadal Stunned, Murray Cruises, Kyrgios Slumps in Shanghai
